    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Die lune qui fuit quartus exeuntis mensis decembris. Predictorum virorum
                        presentia, scilicet <persName><name ref="Robertus/de Gorgo"
                            >Roberti</name></persName> de <placeName>Gurgo</placeName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Martinus/Decanus">Martini
                            Decani</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Martinus/Pizolus">Martini
                                Pizoli</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Iordanus/de Gherardus Paliarius">Iordanis</name></persName> de
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus/Paliarius">Girardo
                            Paliario</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Iohannes/Tosus"
                                >Iohannis Tosi</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Andreas/de Corno">Andręę</name></persName> de Corno et
                                <persName><name ref="Gherardus/de Baiso">Girardi</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/1514">Baise</placeName> atque <persName
                            key="#Slave"><name ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Slave">servi</rs>
                        <persName key="#Landed_possessions #Feudum #siblingOf #nephew/nieceOf"><name
                                ref="Boso">Bosonis</name></persName> et <persName
                                    key="#siblingOf #nephew/nieceOf #Landed_possessions #Feudum"><name ref="Raginmundus"
                                >Ragimundi</name></persName>, presentia et auctoritate
                        <persName key="#uncle/auntOf"><name ref="Gherardus">Girardi</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/2489">Campitello</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#uncle/auntOf">patrui</rs> ipsius Bosonis et Ragimundi. Idem
                        Ragimundus refutavit et finem fecit in manu domni <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Monasteries" ref="#people/3568">Hæinrici</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Landed_possessions #Curtes #Monks #Altars"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, per se suumque
                            <rs key="#siblingOf">fratrem minorem</rs>, adstante predicto Bosone
                        fratre suo, de tota predicta <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs> quam
                        Ugo pater eius dicebat se pro <rs key="#Feudum">feodo</rs> tenere in
                        territorio Sancti Benedicti, ab ista parte <rs key="#Rivers">fluminis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers">Padi Vetuli</placeName>, et ab illa parte ipsius
                        fluminis, in <geogName key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Feudum"
                            ref="#estates/80"><rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Curtes #Landed_possessions #Feudum" ref="#places/362"
                                >Vilule</placeName></geogName> loco
                        <placeName ref="#places/362">Seregnano</placeName>, sive aliis locis ipsius curtis, ex parte
                            <persName key="#childOf #parentOf #Feudum">Ugonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf">Manfredi</persName> et <persName
                            key="#childOf #parentOf #Feudum">Ubaldi</persName> filii eius atque
                            <persName key="#childOf #Feudum">Ugolini</persName> filii Ubaldi, sive
                        aliquo modo, secundum quod predictus Boso frater eius firmaverat in manu
                        predicti domni Hæinrici abbatis, sub eadem poena et defensione, si aliquid
                        impedimentum ipso monasterio de ipsa terra ipse Ragimundus suique fratres
                        eorumque hæredes vel aliqua persona facient. Et propter hanc refutationem et
                        finem acceperunt ipsi fratres Ragimundus et Boso, ex parte domni abbatis,
                            <rs key="#Price">octo libras denariorum Mediolanensium</rs>. Actum est
                        hoc <placeName ref="#places/2400">iuxta cameram domni abbatis</placeName> et
                        in capitulo, ante <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> ipsius monasterii et supra
                            <rs key="#Altars">altare</rs> Sancti Benedicti. Anno dominice
                        incarnationis millesimo centesimo trigesimo secundo, predicto die, inditione
                        decima. (SN) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer" ref="#people/3573"
                            >Bonus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> his interfui, rogatus <rs key="#Writer"
                            >scripsi</rs>. </ab>
